description:
Avengers Arena Volume 1

A Marvel NOW! title. Trapped on an isolated island, 16 superhuman young adults (including cult faves like members of The Runaways, The Avengers Academy and Darkhawk) are given a chilling ultimatum by their demented captor: Fight or die...only one will walk out alive! The series concluded with issue 18 and received a new series named Avengers Undercover, by the same creative team. That series dealt with the consequences of this series.

Written by Dennis Hopeless (#1-12, #14-18) and Christos Gage (#13)

Art by Kevin Walker (#1-3, #5-6, #8-9, #12, #14-15, #17-18), Alessandro Vitti (#4, #7), Riccardo Burchielli (#10-11), and Karl Moline (#13, #16)

Collected Editions

  • Vol. 1: Kill or Die (#1-6)
  • Vol. 2: Game On (#7-12)
  • Vol. 3: Boss Level (#13-18)

Translated into Spanish.
name: Avengers Arena
